Class NamingUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.datamodel.odata.utility.NamingUtils

  • @Beta
public final class NamingUtils
extends Object
    Utility class, that bundles various naming related operations. This class is meant for internal usage only.
